 \nadharm\xc4\x81bhibhav\xc4\x81t k\xe1\xb9\x9b\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\x87a pradu\xe1\xb9\xa3yanti kulastriya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nstr\xc4\xab\xe1\xb9\xa3u du\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xad\xc4\x81su v\xc4\x81r\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\x87eya j\xc4\x81yate var\xe1\xb9\x87asa\xe1\xb9\x85kara\xe1\xb8\xa5 1.41  \n  \nsa\xe1\xb9\x85karo narak\xc4\x81yaiva kulaghn\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 kulasya ca  \npatanti pitaro hy e\xe1\xb9\xa3\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 luptapi\xe1\xb9\x87\xe1\xb8\x8dodakakriy\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 1.42  \n  \ndo\xe1\xb9\xa3air etai\xe1\xb8\xa5 kulaghn\xc4\x81n\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 var\xe1\xb9\x87asa\xe1\xb9\x85karak\xc4\x81rakai\xe1\xb8\xa5  \nuts\xc4\x81dyante j\xc4\x81tidharm\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 kuladharm\xc4\x81\xc5\x9b ca \xc5\x9b\xc4\x81\xc5\x9bvat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 1.43  \n  \nutsannakuladharm\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 manu\xe1\xb9\xa3y\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x83 jan\xc4\x81rdana  \nnarake niyata\xe1\xb9\x83 v\xc4\x81so bhavat\xc4\xabty anu\xc5\x9bu\xc5\x9bruma 1.44  \n  \naho bata mahat p\xc4\x81pa\xe1\xb9\x83 kartu\xe1\xb9\x83 vyavasit\xc4\x81 vayam  \nyad r\xc4\x81jyasukhalobhena hantu\xe1\xb9\x83 svajanam udyat\xc4\x81\xe1\xb8\xa5 1.45  \n  \nyadi m\xc4\x81m aprat\xc4\xabk\xc4\x81ram a\xc5\x9bastra\xe1\xb9\x83 \xc5\x9bastrap\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x87aya\xe1\xb8\xa5  \ndh\xc4\x81rtar\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\xa3\xe1\xb9\xadr\xc4\x81 ra\xe1\xb9\x87e hanyus tan me k\xe1\xb9\xa3ematara\xe1\xb9\x83 bhavet  \n1.46  \n  \nevam uktv\xc4\x81rjuna\xe1\xb8\xa5 sa\xe1\xb9\x85khye rathopastha up\xc4\x81vi\xc5\x9bat  \nvis\xe1\xb9\x9bjya sa\xc5\x9bara\xe1\xb9\x83 c\xc4\x81pa\xe1\xb9\x83 \xc5\x9bokasa\xe1\xb9\x83vignam\xc4\x81nasa\xe1\xb8\xa5 1.47  \n  \n  \n\n* * *\n\n[Next: II. atha dvit\xc4\xabyodhy\xc4\x81ya\xe1\xb8\xa5. (s\xc4\x81\xe1\xb9\x85khyayoga\xe1\xb8\xa5)](bgs02.htm)\n\n'